= OpenGL tests for IA signals =

== Introduction ==

This directory contains an OpenGL program which can be useful to test
IA signals mainly because it uses a large number of vertices through
a Vertex Buffer Object.

== Compilation ==

Please, read the INSTALL file in src/.

== Results ==

Tested on NV98.

input_assembler_busy: ~12%
input_assembler_waits_for_fb : ~57%
